<HEAD>Three Men Get Life For Beheading `Wizard'</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MANILA, Philippines (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A court sentenced three men to life
in prison for beheading a farmer they thought was a wizard, the
Philippines News Agency said Friday.
   A court in the central city of Cebu returned the sentences
Thursday for Elanito Quijano, 25; Edwin Layug, 23; and Danilo
Lapinid, 24, the state-run news agency reported.
